# Packed — design rules

Full reference: `STYLE_GUIDE.md`, `registry/styles/packed-theme-tokens.css`.
Non-negotiable — do not reintroduce framework defaults (cool-grey ramps,
hard-black shadows, sharp corners).

## The one rule
**Tokens are the contract.** Never hard-code a hex, px, font, or shadow. Reference
semantic tokens (`--brand`, `--text-muted`, `--grad-cta`), not raw scale steps.

## Color
- Warm, sunset-led. Brand orange `#FF6B2C` (`--brand`) anchors actions and logo.
  Sky blue `#2B8CD9` (`--accent`) is reserved for weather / sky / flight-status.
- Warm sand neutrals (cream `--bg-app`, white cards). **No cool grey, no pure black**
  — never introduce `gray-*`.
- **Proportion 70/20/10:** cream + white first, one orange for action, blue sparingly.
- Utility hues are functional only (status fg/bg pairs).
- Gradients on heroes/CTAs only — not resting surfaces.

## Type
- **Lora** — display/headlines (600, `-0.02em`). Never body/UI in serif.
- **Figtree** — all UI/body (300–800). Body line-height 1.65.
- **DM Mono** — numbers, times, flight codes, gates.
- Sentence case; ALL-CAPS only for `.pk-eyebrow`.
- Fonts via `@fontsource` — no runtime CDN.

## Spacing · radius · borders
- Spacing: 4px base unit. Scale: 4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 20 / 24 / 32 / 40 / 48 / 64 / 80 / 96.
- Radius: soft — inputs/buttons 12, cards 16, hero 20–28, pills full.
- Borders: 1px `--border-subtle`/`--border-default`; form controls 1.5px → `--border-brand` on focus.

## Elevation
- Warm-tinted shadows via role aliases (`--elev-card`, `--elev-popover`, `--elev-modal`).
- Glass/blur only for floating chrome over content — never decorative.

## Motion
- `--dur-fast 120ms`, `--dur-base 200ms`, `--dur-slow 320ms`. Nothing harsh.
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.

## States
- Hover: `--brand` → `--brand-hover`, lift `-1px`; ghost → `--brand-subtle`.
- Press: settles back. No colour inversion.
- Focus: `--ring-focus` halo at `--ring-width 3px`.

## Voice (for any UI copy)
- Warm, calm, quietly capable. **You** / **we**. Sentence case. No emoji.
- ✅ "Heads up — your gate just moved to B7."
- ❌ "ALERT: Gate reassignment event detected."

## Iconography
- Lucide, stroke **2**, currentColor. Sizes 16/20/24. No emoji as icons.

## Logo
- `@packed/logo` from the registry. Never below 24px.

## Registry
- `"@packed": "https://ui.trypacked.dev/r/{name}.json"`
- Theme first: `bunx shadcn@latest add @packed/theme`
